  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "SOCIAL MEDIA EXECUTIVE",
  "description": "<p>We are seeking a creative and proactive Social Media Executive to join our marketing team and take ownership of our social media presence on Facebook, Instagram and TikTok. The ideal candidate will have a passion for social media trends, content creation, and community engagement.</p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><p>Manage and grow the company’s social media channels (Facebook, Instagram & TikTok)</p><p>Plan, schedule and publish engaging content (static posts, videos, stories)</p><p>Monitor trends, platform changes and propose new creative campaigns</p><p>Respond to comments, messages and community interactions professionally</p><p>Work with the marketing team on campaigns, product launches and promotions</p><p>Track performance metrics (reach, engagement, growth) and prepare reports</p><p>Support ad campaign execution and optimisation where applicable</p><p>Skills & Experience</p><p>Diploma or degree in Marketing, Communications, Media or related field</p><p>1–3 years of experience in social media management (in-house or agency)</p><p>No experience but with great skills will be considered</p><p>Strong written communication and creative skills</p><p>Proficient with social media tools and analytics</p><p>Able to use AI proficiently is a must</p><p>Self-motivated, organised, and team-oriented</p><p>Full-time/Part-time</p><p>SGD 2,500 – SGD 5,000 per month for similar roles, with variation based on responsibilities and company size</p><p>(Actual offer will depend on candidate experience and skills.)</p><p>Preferred / Advantageous Certificates</p><p>(Not mandatory, but preferred)</p><p>Meta (Facebook) Social Media or Digital Marketing Certificates</p><p>TikTok Academy Certificate</p><p>Google Digital Marketing & E-Commerce Certification</p><p>Google Analytics Certification</p><p>HubSpot Social Media or Content Marketing Certification</p><p>Canva or Adobe Creative Cloud (Photoshop / Premiere)</p><p>Applications without portfolio or work examples may not be considered. <br /></p><p>EA LICENSE 06C4414 / R1107000</p>",
